"屌完免我佣就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e845bbdde15fa4a48cc90d9d5d62da826eef657","tid":229790,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:17:41.000Z","msg":"呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問"},{"pid":"14aa84a26b42dde3fd5c24d3227e55eb1afe0afa","tid":229790,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲  日本仆果次街我諗佢都未撚知樓價係咩一回事"},{"pid":"58595650fef0789e382e270257420f61d45d3fc1","tid":229790,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78f906e175012565e1667c611e4dfb046c9ef227","tid":229790,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T01:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用無窮無盡黎形容樓市，連登仔想人點答？比位你入？<br />\n5年前，10年前，15年前，我都認為樓價會跌，而家同成班連登仔一樣，等緊"},{"pid":"eea76aa77b1ec94e9e70b9c9739b373308e8ec1a","tid":229790,"uid":80819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講真係無窮無盡<br />\n<br />\n以前5毫子 一枝可樂，而家幾錢丫。<br />\n<br />\nN年後10蚊一枝 100蚊一枝都有可能"},{"pid":"ce9a4bef44ba9cc0a227e6ba5c71bae71cdcfde3","tid":229790,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長遠黎講真係無窮無盡<br />\n<br />\n以前5毫子 一枝可樂，而家幾錢丫。<br />\n<br />\nN年後10蚊一枝 100蚊一枝都有可能</blockquote><br />\n講咁多做咩呀，租樓日日賺喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c36c90f5fd099d0ea93d4de6926c618e90f7fc9","tid":229790,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:18:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺下之意你嘅生命無窮無盡? 如果覺得自己準，下個月跌五成，去沽空新雄雞，長實，狗鐵.....等地產股，地產股唔得即係連帶銀行都唔得，大手沽空佢包發達"},{"pid":"e7f63cccb724930fd1a5d9584f173f594679c9a3","tid":229790,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T02:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲新聞上連登死撚硬，必被群空批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：工作關係參加左德國某工業展拎過獎，拒絕過HKET 訪問</blockquote><br />\n閣下之意覺得香港樓可升到無窮無盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">閣</span>下之意你嘅生命無窮無盡? 如果覺得自己準，下個月跌五成，去沽空新雄雞，長實，狗鐵.....等地產股，地產股唔得即係連帶銀行都唔得，大手沽空佢包發達</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7b5e816cb68a5b289eef894c32195ffc70d57661","tid":229790,"uid":80819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c